query:
SELECT 
  dealMachinePropertyId,
  streetAddress,
  city,
  state,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM contacts WHERE contacts.propertyId = properties.id) as contact_count,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM contactPhones WHERE contactPhones.contactId IN (SELECT id FROM contacts WHERE contacts.propertyId = properties.id)) as phone_count,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM contactEmails WHERE contactEmails.contactId IN (SELECT id FROM contacts WHERE contacts.propertyId = properties.id)) as email_count
FROM properties 
WHERE dealMachinePropertyId IN ('1238558064', '1238558191', '1238558333', '1267547430', '1267547553', '1267547891', '1267548239', '1267548524', '1267548596', '1267549028')
ORDER BY dealMachinePropertyId;
